Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and 'Request Payment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average waiting time to the 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time it takes 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to be redone
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE occurs

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Average time for 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' grouped by 'org:resource'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and the end of case grouped by the last value of org:resource

Name: Total time for 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' in cases leading to 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time it takes from 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Time until 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' after 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Elapsed time between 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and next 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Time from 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' in cases where it occurs
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'
